query.sfwSql: select dro.*,per.MPI_PERSON_ID as ParticipantMPID,pas.MPI_PERSON_ID as PayeeMPID, per.FIRST_NAME as ParticipantFirstName, per.LAST_NAME as ParticipantLastName,ISNULL(per.VIP_FLAG,'N') as istrRelativeVipFlag, pas.FIRST_NAME as PayeeFirstName, pas.LAST_NAME as PayeeLastName ,dro_ben.PLAN_ID, sgt_plan.PLAN_NAME istrPlan, dro_ben.DRO_MODEL_VALUE , (select DESCRIPTION from SGS_CODE_VALUE where CODE_VALUE = DRO_MODEL_VALUE and CODE_ID = DRO_MODEL_ID) istrDROModel from SGT_DRO_APPLICATION as dro WITH(NOLOCK) left join SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS as dro_ben WITH(NOLOCK) on dro_ben.DRO_APPLICATION_ID=dro.DRO_APPLICATION_ID inner join SGT_PERSON as per WITH(NOLOCK) on per.PERSON_ID=dro.PERSON_ID inner join SGT_PERSON as pas WITH(NOLOCK) on pas.PERSON_ID=dro.ALTERNATE_PAYEE_ID left join sgt_plan on SGT_PLAN.PLAN_ID = dro_ben.PLAN_ID
select * from SGT_PERSON WITH(NOLOCK) where MPI_PERSON_ID in (@person_mpi_id,@payee_mpi_id)

select COUNT(*) from SGT_DRO_APPLICATION dro WITH(NOLOCK) join SGT_PERSON per WITH(NOLOCK) on per.PERSON_ID=dro.PERSON_ID join SGT_PERSON p WITH(NOLOCK) on p.PERSON_ID=dro.ALTERNATE_PAYEE_ID where dro.DRO_STATUS_VALUE!='CNLD' And DRO_STATUS_VALUE != 'QLFD' and DRO_STATUS_VALUE != 'AMQL' and per.MPI_PERSON_ID=@person_mpid and p.MPI_PERSON_ID=@alternate_payee_mpid
select COUNT(*) from SGT_DRO_APPLICATION WITH(NOLOCK) where DRO_STATUS_VALUE ! = 'QLFD' and DRO_STATUS_VALUE ! = 'CNLD' and PERSON_ID=@person_id and dro_application_id != @dro_application_id
select * from SGT_DRO_APPLICATION WITH(NOLOCK) where JOINDER_ON_FILE='Y' and QUALIFIED_DATE is null and BATCH_90DAY_FLAG='N' and DATEDIFF(DAY,JOINDER_RECV_DATE,GETDATE()) > @no_of_days
select COUNT(*) from SGT_DRO_APPLICATION WITH(NOLOCK) where (DRO_STATUS_VALUE = 'QLFD' or DRO_STATUS_VALUE = 'AMQL') and alternate_payee_id=@alternate_payee_id
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_DRO_APPLICATION DRO WHERE (DRO_STATUS_VALUE='QLFD' OR DRO_STATUS_VALUE ='AMQL') AND ALTERNATE_PAYEE_ID =@ALTERNATE_PAYEE_ID AND PERSON_ID=@PERSON_ID

select * from SGT_DRO_APPLICATION sda join SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS sdbd on sdbd.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = sda.DRO_APPLICATION_ID join SGT_PERSON sp on sp.PERSON_ID = sda.PERSON_ID join SGT_PERSON spAlt on spAlt.PERSON_ID = sda.ALTERNATE_PAYEE_ID where sp.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID and spAlt.PERSON_ID = @ALT_PAYEE_ID and (sda.DRo_STATUS_VALUE = 'QLFD' OR sda.DRo_STATUS_VALUE = 'AMQL')
SELECT * FROM SGT_QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER WHERE QDRO_APPLICATION_ID = @QDRO_APPLICATION_ID AND STATUS_VALUE <> 'CANC'
select (FIRST_NAME +' '+LAST_NAME ) as 'UserName' from SGS_USER where USER_ID =@approved_by_user

SELECT SDBD.PLAN_ID, SDA.DRO_STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA LEFT JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE SDA.DRO_STATUS_VALUE IN ('AMQL','RCVD') AND SDA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID

SELECT SPA.* FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR SPBX ON SPA.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SPBX.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID WHERE (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID =SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.MODIFIED_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL','CNCL') AND SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID IS NULL AND SPA.DRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL_ID IS NULL AND SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE IN ('RTMT','DSBL') AND SPA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SPBX.PLAN_ID = @PLAN_ID
SELECT BENEFIT_AMOUNT FROM SGT_BENEFIT_CALCULATION_OPTIONS WHERE BENEFIT_CALCULATION_DETAIL_ID = @BENEFIT_CALCULATION_DETAIL_ID

SELECT SUM(SPARC.IAP_BALANCE_AMOUNT) FROM SGT_PERSON SP INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT SPA ON SP.PERSON_ID = SPA.PERSON_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_RETIREMENT_CONTRIBUTION SPARC ON SPARC.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE SPA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SPA.PLAN_ID = 1

SELECT DISTINCT SDA.PERSON_ID,SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,SDA.ELIGIBLE_FOR_CONTINUANCE_FLAG FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT (NOLOCK) SPA INNER JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS(NOLOCK) SDBD ON SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_DRO_APPLICATION(NOLOCK) SDA ON SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE = 'STRF' AND SPA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID

SELECT DISTINCT PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PA WHERE PA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND
( SELECT top(1) SPAS.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS SPAS WHERE SPAS.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY MODIFIED_DATE DESC ) NOT IN ('CNCL','CMPL') and (PA.RETIREE_INCR_FLAG <> 'Y' OR PA.RETIREE_INCR_FLAG is NULL)

select * from SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA join SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA on spa.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = spba.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID join SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD on SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID = spa.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID where spa.PERSON_ID <> SPBA.PERSON_ID and SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE = 'STRF' and SPBA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID

select SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID AS DRO_BENEFIT_ID,sdbd.DRO_MODEL_VALUE from SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR SPBX ON SPBX.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD ON SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID AND SPBX.PLAN_ID = SDBD.PLAN_ID JOIN SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'QDRO' and (spa.RETIREE_INCR_FLAG is null or SPA.RETIREE_INCR_FLAG <> 'Y') AND SDA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL','CNCL')

SELECT DISTINCT SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,SPBA.PERSON_ID,SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE, SPA.TERM_CERTAIN_END_DATE,SDA.ELIGIBLE_FOR_CONTINUANCE_FLAG,SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA ON SPA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = SPBA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD ON SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID LEFT OUTER JOIN SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE SPA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND EXISTS(SELECT TOP(1)* FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS SPAS WHERE SPAS.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND SPAS.STATUS_VALUE = 'CMPL' AND TERMINATED_STATUS_REASON_VALUE = 'DETH' ORDER BY MODIFIED_DATE DESC) AND SPA.PERSON_ID <> SPBA.PERSON_ID AND SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE IN ('WDRL','QDRO')

SELECT DISTINCT PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,PA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT PA WHERE PA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND
( SELECT top(1) SPAS.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS SPAS WHERE SPAS.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = PA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY MODIFIED_DATE DESC ) NOT IN ('CNCL','CMPL') AND PA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE IN ('RTMT','DSBL','WDRL')

SELECT SUM(CNT) FROM ( SELECT COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM SGW_WORKFLOW_REQUEST WHERE PROCESS_ID = 1 AND STATUS_VALUE = 'PSNP' AND PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID union SELECT COUNT(*) AS CNT FROM SGW_PROCESS_INSTANCE WHERE PROCESS_ID = 1 AND STATUS_VALUE = 'INPC' AND PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID )AS A

SELECT DISTINCT SQCH.* FROM SGT_QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER SQCH INNER JOIN SGT_QDRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL SQCD ON SQCH.QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER_ID = SQCD.QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER_ID WHERE SQCH.STATUS_VALUE <> 'CANC' AND CALCULATION_TYPE_VALUE = 'FINL' AND SQCD.QDRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = @QDRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID

SELECT SPA.PERSON_ID, SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD WITH(NOLOCK) ON SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID WHERE (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL', 'CNCL') AND SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = @DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA INNER JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE = 'STRF' AND SDA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SDA.DRO_STATUS_VALUE <> 'CNLD'

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA INNER JOIN SGT_QDRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL SQCD ON SPA.DRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL_ID = SQCD.QDRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL_ID WHERE SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'QDRO' AND SQCD.REFERENECE_PARTICIPANT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = @PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL', 'CNCL')

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER SQCH INNER JOIN SGT_QDRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL SQCD ON SQCH.QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER_ID = SQCD.QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER_ID WHERE SQCH.QDRO_APPLICATION_ID = @QDRO_APPLICATION_ID AND SQCD.QDRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = @QDRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID AND SQCD.REFERENECE_PARTICIPANT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = @PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID AND SQCH.STATUS_VALUE <> 'CANC'

SELECT DISTINCT SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA INNER JOIN SGT_WITHHOLDING_INFORMATION SWI ON SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SWI.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE SWI.WITHHOLDING_DATE_TO IS NULL AND SPA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID

SELECT SPA.PERSON_ID, SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD WITH(NOLOCK) ON SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID WHERE (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) IN ('CMPL') AND SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = @DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID

SELECT DISTINCT SQCD.REFERENECE_PARTICIPANT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID FROM SGT_QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER SQCH INNER JOIN SGT_QDRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL SQCD ON SQCH.QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER_ID = SQCD.QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER_ID WHERE SQCH.STATUS_VALUE = 'CANC' AND CALCULATION_TYPE_VALUE = 'FINL' AND SQCD.QDRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = @QDRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID

SELECT DISTINCT SPA.* FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA INNER JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD ON SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE SDA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'QDRO' AND (SELECT TOP(1)STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL','CNCL') AND (SDA.ELIGIBLE_FOR_CONTINUANCE_FLAG <> 'Y' OR SDA.ELIGIBLE_FOR_CONTINUANCE_FLAG = NULL) AND (SPA.RETIREE_INCR_FLAG <> 'Y' OR SPA.RETIREE_INCR_FLAG IS NULL)

SELECT SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID,JOINT_ANNUITANT_ID FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA WITH(NOLOCK) INNER JOIN SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL SBAD ON SPA.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID = SBAD.BENEFIT_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID WHERE SPA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL', 'CNCL') AND BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE IN ('RTMT','DSBL') AND SBAD.JOINT_ANNUITANT_ID IS NOT NULL AND SBAD.JOINT_ANNUITANT_ID > 0 AND (SPA.RETIREE_INCR_FLAG <> 'Y' OR SPA.RETIREE_INCR_FLAG IS NULL)

SELECT Distinct SR.* FROM SGT_RELATIONSHIP SR INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT_BENEFICIARY SPAB ON SR.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID = SPAB.PERSON_RELATIONSHIP_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PERSON_ACCOUNT SPA ON SPA.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID = SPAB.PERSON_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE SR.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SR.BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID = @BENEFICIARY_PERSON_ID AND SPA.PLAN_ID = @PLAN_ID AND SR.RELATIONSHIP_VALUE = 'EXSP'

SELECT Count(*) FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA ON SPA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = SPBA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'QDRO' AND (SELECT TOP 1 Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WITH(NOLOCK) WHERE Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) IN ('CMPL') AND SPBA.PERSON_ID = @ParticipantPERSON_ID

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA WHERE SPA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SPA.RETIREMENT_TYPE_VALUE IN ('REDE','SPLR','URED') AND SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'RTMT' AND (SELECT top(1) SPAS.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS SPAS WHERE SPAS.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY MODIFIED_DATE DESC) = 'CMPL' AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM SGT_BENEFIT_APPLICATION SBA WHERE SBA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SBA.BENEFIT_TYPE_VALUE='DSBL' AND SBA.APPLICATION_STATUS_VALUE = 'PEND')

SELECT DISTINCT SPA.* FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA ON SPA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = SPBA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR SPBX ON SPA.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SPBX.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID WHERE SPBA.PERSON_ID = @PARCIPANT_ID AND SPA.PERSON_ID = @ALTERNATE_ID AND SPBX.PLAN_ID = @PLAN_ID AND SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'QDRO' AND (SELECT top(1) SPAS.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS SPAS WHERE SPAS.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY MODIFIED_DATE DESC) = 'CMPL'

SELECT DISTINCT SPA.*,(SELECT TOP(1) STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WHERE SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY Q.STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) AS STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA ON SPA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = SPBA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID WHERE SPBA.PERSON_ID = @PARTICIPANT_ID AND SPA.PERSON_ID = @ALTERNATE_PAYEE_ID AND SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'QDRO' AND (RETIREE_INCR_FLAG <> 'Y' OR RETIREE_INCR_FLAG IS NULL)
SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_QDRO_CALCULATION_HEADER WHERE QDRO_APPLICATION_ID = @QDRO_APPLICATION_ID AND STATUS_VALUE = 'PEND'

select * from SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE DRO_STATUS_VALUE = 'QLFD' AND PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SDBD.PLAN_ID = @PLAN_ID

select * from SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD ON SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID WHERE DRO_STATUS_VALUE NOT IN ('CNLD') AND PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SDA.ALTERNATE_PAYEE_ID = @ALTERNATE_PAYEE_ID and SDBD.DRO_MODEL_VALUE = 'STRF' and SDBD.PLAN_ID = @PLAN_ID

SELECT COUNT(*) FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT SPBA ON SPA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID = SPBA.PAYEE_BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PLAN_BENEFIT_XR SPBX ON SPBX.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID = SPA.PLAN_BENEFIT_ID WHERE SPA.BENEFIT_ACCOUNT_TYPE_VALUE = 'QDRO' AND SPA.DRO_CALCULATION_DETAIL_ID IS NULL AND (SELECT TOP(1)Q.STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT_STATUS Q WHERE SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID = Q.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID ORDER BY STATUS_EFFECTIVE_DATE DESC) NOT IN ('CMPL','CNCL') AND SPBA.PERSON_ID = @PERSON_ID AND SPBX.PLAN_ID = @PLAN_ID

--PIR 924 SELECT COUNT(Distinct SPHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID) AS PAYMENT_COUNT FROM SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DISTRIBUTION SPHD INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER SPHH ON SPHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID=SPHD.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYEE_ACCOUNT SPA on SPHH.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID=SPA.PAYEE_ACCOUNT_ID INNER JOIN SGT_DRO_BENEFIT_DETAILS SDBD on SDBD.DRO_BENEFIT_ID=SPA.DRO_APPLICATION_DETAIL_ID INNER JOIN SGT_DRO_APPLICATION SDA on SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID=SDBD.DRO_APPLICATION_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_HISTORY_DETAIL SPED on SPED.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID=SPHH.PAYMENT_HISTORY_HEADER_ID INNER JOIN SGT_PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE PIT on PIT.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID = SPED.PAYMENT_ITEM_TYPE_ID where SPHD.DISTRIBUTION_STATUS_VALUE NOT IN ('CNLD','RCMD') AND SDA.DRO_APPLICATION_ID = @DRO_APPLICATION_ID HAVING SUM(ISNULL(SPED.AMOUNT,0) * PIT.ITEM_TYPE_DIRECTION) > 0
SELECT DRO_STATUS_VALUE FROM SGT_DRO_APPLICATION with(nolock) WHERE PERSON_ID = @PersonId AND DRO_STATUS_VALUE NOT IN ('CNCL')
